WEBVTT

01:30.860 --> 01:34.950
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.570 --> 01:39.460
[2020]

01:35.640 --> 01:37.120
Come on, everyone, take a look

01:37.120 --> 01:39.150
at the sales performance
for the last 3 months.

01:39.150 --> 01:40.759
Liu Yun is ranked first.

01:40.870 --> 01:42.200
Li Xiaohong is second.

01:42.920 --> 01:44.120
He Cong is third.

01:44.750 --> 01:46.550
-Xia Xiaolan, you...
-Ms. Qian.

01:46.840 --> 01:48.570
I have something to ask Ms. Liu.

01:49.710 --> 01:51.240
Ms. Liu, I would like to ask,

01:51.590 --> 01:52.759
why before every meeting,

01:52.759 --> 01:54.479
you'd assign me temporary tasks,

01:54.479 --> 01:55.280
using small accounts

01:55.280 --> 01:56.610
to fill up my work hours.

01:56.840 --> 01:58.280
In the end,
the clients I bring to sign deals

01:58.280 --> 01:59.509
become your performance figures—

01:59.509 --> 02:00.590
may I ask why?

02:00.920 --> 02:01.790
Xiaolan,

02:02.040 --> 02:03.700
is there a misunderstanding?

02:06.680 --> 02:07.610
Calm down first.

02:07.950 --> 02:09.210
Let's talk privately.

02:10.680 --> 02:11.240
No need.

02:11.520 --> 02:12.450
Let's say it now.

02:12.460 --> 02:13.670
I hate green tea.

02:15.490 --> 02:18.230
[Episode 5:
A Villain Shouldn't Talk Too Much]

02:18.750 --> 02:19.840
You're right.

02:20.150 --> 02:21.030
But in the future,

02:21.030 --> 02:22.430
more and more people

02:22.430 --> 02:22.910
will be willing to pay

02:22.910 --> 02:24.310
for these fancy clothes.

02:24.310 --> 02:26.440
This is a business opportunity for us.

02:28.840 --> 02:30.470
You can predict the future?

02:33.430 --> 02:35.630
Then what do you want to switch lines to?

02:36.079 --> 02:37.940
I want to switch lines to butchering pigs.

02:37.940 --> 02:39.310
I have martial arts skills.

02:39.310 --> 02:41.110
So butchering is easy to pick up.

02:43.880 --> 02:46.680
Have you thought about
going to the special economic zone

02:46.680 --> 02:47.480
to take a look?

02:47.720 --> 02:49.430
You mean
the Shengcheng Special Economic Zone?

02:49.430 --> 02:52.020
You need a Border Permit to go there.

02:52.630 --> 02:54.360
But it's all just
construction sites there.

02:54.360 --> 02:55.490
It's a mess.

02:55.520 --> 02:56.590
If I go there,

02:56.710 --> 02:58.030
what business could I do?

02:58.030 --> 02:59.430
Go take a look if you get the chance.

02:59.430 --> 03:00.470
Maybe you'll really find

03:00.470 --> 03:02.200
some business opportunities.

03:02.750 --> 03:03.190
Okay.

03:03.630 --> 03:05.560
I'll go take a look when I have time.

03:06.310 --> 03:07.280
So when will you

03:07.280 --> 03:08.400
come back again to Longcheng?

03:08.400 --> 03:09.870
We'll meet again
when fate brings us together.

03:09.870 --> 03:11.400
I'm heading to the station.

03:11.560 --> 03:13.240
You can check in these goods.

03:13.430 --> 03:14.600
You didn't know, right?

03:14.600 --> 03:15.840
I know the train station well.

03:15.840 --> 03:16.640
I'll take you.

03:16.680 --> 03:18.680
Please watch my stall for a bit.

03:18.680 --> 03:19.710
I'll be right back.

03:19.710 --> 03:20.520
Really, no need.

03:20.520 --> 03:21.310
I can go by myself.

03:21.310 --> 03:22.190
No need.

03:22.680 --> 03:23.770
Let me take it.

03:25.030 --> 03:26.490
Buy some other things too.

03:26.590 --> 03:27.250
Take a look.

03:32.000 --> 03:32.710
Oh my.

03:33.470 --> 03:34.760
People outside these days

03:34.760 --> 03:36.220
dress like this?

03:36.829 --> 03:38.680
They wear such stylish clothes.

03:39.030 --> 03:40.560
Look how colorful they are.

03:42.520 --> 03:43.000
-This one.
-Auntie.

03:43.000 --> 03:44.200
You look good in this.

03:44.960 --> 03:46.420
This color suits you well.

03:46.590 --> 03:48.190
Isn't this too youthful for me?

03:48.190 --> 03:48.990
It looks good.

03:49.240 --> 03:49.590
Well...

03:49.590 --> 03:51.079
-Xiaolan is back.
-Does it suit me?

03:51.079 --> 03:51.520
Mom.

03:51.870 --> 03:52.750
Why didn't you send a telegram?

03:52.750 --> 03:53.860
I would have picked you up.

03:53.860 --> 03:55.590
No need. I just carried it back.

03:56.079 --> 03:57.190
Look, Xiaolan brought back

03:57.190 --> 03:58.310
such colorful clothes.

03:58.310 --> 03:58.910
Look.

03:59.000 --> 03:59.520
Well...

03:59.800 --> 04:01.000
This is so much stock.

04:01.360 --> 04:03.360
You spent all the money you brought?

04:03.750 --> 04:04.680
Of course.

04:04.800 --> 04:05.960
It's rare that I get to go there.

04:05.960 --> 04:07.620
It'd be a waste not to stock up.

04:11.340 --> 04:12.070
Look at this.

04:15.340 --> 04:16.630
Look at this little button.

04:16.630 --> 04:17.040
Yeah.

04:18.190 --> 04:19.240
It really is nice.

04:21.120 --> 04:23.050
Where are we going to sell all this?

04:23.560 --> 04:24.490
There is a place.

04:28.010 --> 04:28.950
Look at this.

04:30.020 --> 04:31.080
There's more here.

04:35.360 --> 04:36.000
Xiaolan.

04:36.830 --> 04:38.120
Working in these shoes

04:38.120 --> 04:39.390
is too uncomfortable.

04:39.430 --> 04:40.310
Mom, trust me.

04:40.310 --> 04:41.640
It looks good like this.

04:42.630 --> 04:43.630
Does it look good?

04:43.640 --> 04:44.840
Then this sweater...

04:45.240 --> 04:46.310
Hang it over there.

04:50.200 --> 04:52.150
Don't miss out!

04:52.170 --> 04:53.630
Goods from Longcheng!

04:53.630 --> 04:55.000
Come take a look!

04:56.159 --> 04:56.750
Xiaolan.

04:57.190 --> 04:58.920
Why does everything end in 9.9?

04:59.240 --> 05:00.360
This 19.9

05:00.360 --> 05:02.040
is only a dime less than 20.

05:02.090 --> 05:02.820
But that 1 dime

05:02.820 --> 05:04.200
makes it much more tempting.

05:04.200 --> 05:04.680
Get it?

05:08.360 --> 05:08.830
Miss.

05:08.920 --> 05:10.220
Look at these jeans.

05:10.360 --> 05:12.240
-They're from Longcheng.
-Xiaoqin!

05:12.240 --> 05:12.750
Come on.

05:12.920 --> 05:13.830
New arrivals today.

05:13.830 --> 05:15.160
Come again!

05:16.830 --> 05:17.430
Xiaolan.

05:18.070 --> 05:19.330
There are many buyers,

05:19.390 --> 05:20.800
but there are many sellers too.

05:20.800 --> 05:21.270
Mom.

05:21.600 --> 05:23.560
Our target customers

05:23.800 --> 05:25.390
aren't factory girls,

05:25.680 --> 05:26.810
but office workers.

05:27.000 --> 05:27.600
They...

05:27.600 --> 05:29.360
not only care about style,

05:29.560 --> 05:31.160
but also have aesthetic demands.

05:31.160 --> 05:31.800
Look.

05:32.240 --> 05:34.040
Over there is the City Hall.

05:34.190 --> 05:35.390
Here is the farmers' market.

05:35.390 --> 05:36.830
Past this is the Department Store.

05:36.830 --> 05:37.920
So on their commute,

05:37.570 --> 05:41.310
[City Hall] [Farmers' Market] [Us] [Department Store]

05:38.159 --> 05:39.040
they have to pass by here.

05:39.040 --> 05:39.560
Right?

05:41.600 --> 05:42.400
I have an idea.

05:47.040 --> 05:47.750
Mom, Mom.

05:48.600 --> 05:49.560
Put this on.

05:50.000 --> 05:50.560
Me?

05:51.390 --> 05:52.950
No way. It's too gaudy. I...

05:52.950 --> 05:54.310
Mom, do you trust me?

05:54.950 --> 05:56.010
I trust you, but...

05:56.020 --> 05:56.750
Listen to me.

05:57.000 --> 05:57.950
Put this on.

05:58.310 --> 05:59.120
Just go to the places I mentioned

05:59.120 --> 06:00.320
and walk around a bit.

06:00.390 --> 06:01.160
Xiaolan...

06:01.480 --> 06:02.310
Well... Well...

06:02.310 --> 06:03.640
-What's this for?
-Mom.

06:03.830 --> 06:04.630
Be confident.

06:04.800 --> 06:06.400
Confidence makes you shine.

06:08.240 --> 06:09.000
Okay.

06:09.190 --> 06:10.250
I'll listen to you.

06:11.160 --> 06:12.360
How much for this one?

06:12.470 --> 06:13.600
The price is marked.

06:13.920 --> 06:14.920
9.9 each.

06:15.040 --> 06:15.800
9.9?

06:16.680 --> 06:17.800
Let me think about it.

06:17.800 --> 06:18.800
Sure, no problem.

06:19.270 --> 06:20.200
Come back again.

06:20.310 --> 06:20.720
Okay.

06:26.560 --> 06:27.120
Xiaolan!

06:27.430 --> 06:28.000
Xiaolan!

06:28.430 --> 06:29.270
I hadn't even

06:29.430 --> 06:30.830
reached the Department Store

06:30.830 --> 06:32.510
and a few young people
already surrounded me,

06:32.510 --> 06:33.750
asking where I bought this shirt

06:33.750 --> 06:34.800
and pants.

06:35.010 --> 06:36.430
I got scared and ran right back.

06:36.430 --> 06:37.040
Mom, Mom.

06:37.120 --> 06:38.120
Don't be nervous.

06:38.600 --> 06:39.600
Is it over there?

06:39.870 --> 06:40.600
It should be.

06:40.630 --> 06:41.270
Quick, quick.

06:41.270 --> 06:42.070
Here comes business.

06:42.070 --> 06:43.040
Go sit down. Go sit down.

06:43.040 --> 06:43.680
What business?

06:43.680 --> 06:45.070
Let me hang this sign up in the meantime.

06:45.070 --> 06:45.560
Sis.

06:45.750 --> 06:47.270
Did you buy your clothes here?

06:47.270 --> 06:47.840
I... yes.

06:47.870 --> 06:48.510
Yes, yes.

06:48.560 --> 06:49.040
Right here in our shop.

06:49.040 --> 06:49.920
This outfit looks great.

06:49.920 --> 06:50.990
Take a look. Come take a look.

06:50.990 --> 06:52.350
They're all from Longcheng.

06:52.350 --> 06:53.600
How much is this knit top?

06:53.600 --> 06:54.630
You have a great eye.

06:54.630 --> 06:56.000
These are the latest stocks I brought in

06:56.000 --> 06:56.930
from Longcheng.

06:57.000 --> 06:58.360
Prices are labeled.

06:58.430 --> 06:59.950
The ad says 29.90.

07:00.310 --> 07:01.800
The clothes are nice,

07:01.870 --> 07:03.040
but a bit expensive.

07:03.480 --> 07:04.390
Just one sweater

07:04.390 --> 07:05.480
costs a month's salary.

07:05.480 --> 07:06.360
But you have to look at

07:06.360 --> 07:07.360
its material.

07:07.400 --> 07:08.000
Look.

07:08.030 --> 07:09.830
These are precision machine-knitted.

07:09.830 --> 07:11.560
Look how even the stitching is.

07:11.720 --> 07:13.310
You can't get this quality by hand.

07:13.310 --> 07:14.240
In Longcheng, these goods

07:14.240 --> 07:14.870
are all for export

07:14.870 --> 07:15.830
to foreign countries.

07:15.830 --> 07:17.600
It's still a bit too expensive.

07:17.920 --> 07:19.050
It's not expensive.

07:19.070 --> 07:20.560
Our prices are clearly marked.

07:20.560 --> 07:21.600
You don't need to worry others

07:21.600 --> 07:22.830
are paying less than you.

07:22.830 --> 07:24.290
The quality is excellent.

07:24.430 --> 07:26.240
Your viscount for buying a set,

07:26.260 --> 07:27.110
what does that mean?

07:26.300 --> 07:30.300
[Discount]

07:27.270 --> 07:28.920
It's not viscount but discount.

07:28.920 --> 07:29.790
It means

07:30.070 --> 07:31.720
if you buy the top and pants

07:31.720 --> 07:32.390
together,

07:32.390 --> 07:33.310
you get 10% off.

07:33.510 --> 07:35.040
The top is 2.90 cheaper,

07:35.040 --> 07:36.470
and same goes for the pants.

07:36.470 --> 07:37.090
I know.

07:37.120 --> 07:38.310
That's how they do it

07:38.430 --> 07:39.430
in Gangdao movies.

07:39.430 --> 07:40.000
Yes, yes.

07:40.120 --> 07:40.950
You're so stylish.

07:40.950 --> 07:42.120
Exactly, that's it.

07:42.270 --> 07:44.120
All right, give me a set then.

07:44.120 --> 07:45.190
And help me pick a pair of pants.

07:45.190 --> 07:46.270
Sure, let me pick you one.

07:46.270 --> 07:47.870
These two are different colors,

07:47.870 --> 07:48.800
but both look great.

07:48.800 --> 07:49.520
Look at the cut.

07:49.520 --> 07:51.390
Bell-bottoms. You'll look slim in them.

07:51.390 --> 07:52.430
If I

07:52.560 --> 07:54.390
buy with someone else,

07:54.510 --> 07:55.270
do we get the discount?

07:55.270 --> 07:56.190
Of course!

07:56.390 --> 07:57.310
You're so smart.

07:57.310 --> 07:58.570
No problem. Of course.

07:58.750 --> 07:59.270
These pants.

07:59.270 --> 08:00.190
Feel free to look around.

08:00.190 --> 08:00.720
Xiaolan.

08:00.950 --> 08:01.750
Of course.

08:01.870 --> 08:02.720
Take a look.

08:02.720 --> 08:04.000
Well, how about...

08:05.040 --> 08:06.700
I go take another walk around?

08:07.190 --> 08:07.830
Sure, Mom.

08:08.310 --> 08:09.120
Be confident.

08:10.390 --> 08:11.220
This one looks good too.

08:11.220 --> 08:12.430
-Come.
-Let's buy them together.

08:12.430 --> 08:13.510
You want both?

08:13.510 --> 08:14.310
I'll wrap it up for you.

08:14.310 --> 08:15.800
-It'll be...
-That'll be...

08:15.800 --> 08:16.360
45.

08:16.390 --> 08:17.430
That's the discounted price.

08:17.430 --> 08:19.630
Don't miss out!

08:20.390 --> 08:22.390
10% off for sets!

08:22.830 --> 08:23.190
45.

08:23.310 --> 08:23.720
Okay.

08:23.750 --> 08:24.880
Let me bag it for you.

08:27.160 --> 08:28.220
It's so beautiful.

08:31.830 --> 08:33.549
90, 95, 500.

08:34.630 --> 08:37.870
1, 2, 3, 4, 5.

08:39.000 --> 08:40.240
505.40 yuan.

08:41.960 --> 08:43.320
We sold
less than half the stock this time,

08:43.320 --> 08:43.720
but we've already made back

08:43.720 --> 08:44.550
505.40 yuan.

08:44.960 --> 08:46.030
Look at our Xiaolan.

08:46.030 --> 08:47.870
How is she so good at making money?

08:47.870 --> 08:48.440
Auntie,

08:48.890 --> 08:50.050
I don't want to split

08:50.080 --> 08:51.240
the profit we made this time yet.

08:51.240 --> 08:52.240
This way, we can

08:52.240 --> 08:53.550
buy more stock next time.

08:53.550 --> 08:54.290
No problem.

08:54.320 --> 08:55.380
I'll listen to you.

08:55.630 --> 08:57.960
We're not in a rush
to use the money anyway.

08:58.030 --> 08:59.630
Making money is definitely a good thing,

08:59.630 --> 09:01.960
but it can't interfere with your studies.

09:03.240 --> 09:03.910
Yeah.

09:04.200 --> 09:05.930
Why aren't the results out yet?

09:07.270 --> 09:08.130
How about this?

09:08.190 --> 09:09.550
I'll go to No.1 High School tomorrow

09:09.550 --> 09:10.550
and ask Chen Qing.

09:10.790 --> 09:12.440
You two just focus on the stall,

09:12.440 --> 09:12.910
okay?

09:12.910 --> 09:13.710
-Sure.
-Sure.

09:15.080 --> 09:15.480
Mom,

09:15.910 --> 09:17.440
you keep this money for now.

09:17.550 --> 09:18.280
It looks like

09:18.320 --> 09:19.550
we'll have to go to the bank

09:19.550 --> 09:21.080
and open a savings account.

09:24.740 --> 09:29.450
[Anqing No.1 High School]

09:30.150 --> 09:30.680
Comrade.

09:30.910 --> 09:31.440
Comrade.

09:31.670 --> 09:33.000
Who are you looking for?

09:33.070 --> 09:34.200
I'm looking for Chen Qing.

09:34.200 --> 09:35.600
-Which Chen Qing?
-Yeah.

09:36.200 --> 09:37.320
S-Senior class.

09:37.720 --> 09:39.180
He's from Qijing Village.

09:40.240 --> 09:40.960
Miss,

09:41.030 --> 09:42.390
I brought you business.

09:42.390 --> 09:43.630
Can you give me more of a discount?

09:43.630 --> 09:44.750
The discount won't change.

09:44.750 --> 09:45.670
But for old customers,

09:45.670 --> 09:46.240
we'll give you

09:46.240 --> 09:47.360
a free pair of pantyhose each.

09:47.360 --> 09:48.030
How about that?

09:48.030 --> 09:49.510
Sure, sure.

09:49.750 --> 09:50.480
This is good stuff.

09:50.480 --> 09:51.200
This is not bad.

09:51.200 --> 09:52.630
I wore these before; they're comfortable.

09:52.630 --> 09:53.690
Please come again.

09:53.720 --> 09:55.050
Count them to make sure.

09:55.120 --> 09:55.980
Come back soon.

09:56.670 --> 09:57.870
How much is this coat?

09:58.360 --> 09:59.390
The price is marked right there.

09:59.390 --> 10:00.240
29.90.

10:01.030 --> 10:02.390
For a piece of street junk like this,

10:02.390 --> 10:03.030
the price is almost as high as

10:03.030 --> 10:04.030
a department store's?

10:04.030 --> 10:05.510
Only a fool would buy from you.

10:05.510 --> 10:06.080
Why do you speak

10:06.080 --> 10:06.960
so harshly?

10:06.960 --> 10:07.720
Buy it if you want.

10:07.720 --> 10:08.480
If not, just leave.

10:08.480 --> 10:08.870
Exactly.

10:08.870 --> 10:09.550
You're the owner

10:09.550 --> 10:12.120
of the clothing store
across the street, right?

10:12.120 --> 10:13.080
So you're a competitor.

10:13.080 --> 10:14.720
Here to ruin my business, huh?

10:14.720 --> 10:15.510
She really is.

10:15.510 --> 10:16.910
She's the one selling clothes
across the street.

10:16.910 --> 10:18.770
Are you sure you can buy her goods?

10:18.790 --> 10:20.360
We don't know where she came from.

10:20.360 --> 10:21.840
If there's any quality problem,

10:21.840 --> 10:23.240
let's see if you can find her.

10:23.240 --> 10:24.300
-That's true.
-No.

10:24.670 --> 10:25.910
You look unfamiliar.

10:26.260 --> 10:27.720
You won't be gone tomorrow, will you?

10:27.720 --> 10:29.080
-Of course not.
-I don't think so.

10:29.080 --> 10:30.610
I've never seen her before.

10:30.720 --> 10:31.550
Don't even know where she

10:31.550 --> 10:32.480
popped out from.

10:32.750 --> 10:33.750
Dressed like that too.

10:33.750 --> 10:34.670
Who knows if she's from

10:34.670 --> 10:35.480
a decent family.

10:35.480 --> 10:36.550
What nonsense are you talking about?

10:36.550 --> 10:37.960
We are decent people.

10:38.270 --> 10:39.600
Just because you say you're decent

10:39.600 --> 10:40.320
doesn't mean you are.

10:40.320 --> 10:41.030
Get lost!

10:41.550 --> 10:42.480
Shut your trap!

10:42.630 --> 10:43.440
Who are you?

10:43.440 --> 10:44.360
You think this mother and daughter
are easy to bully,

10:44.360 --> 10:44.960
don't you?

10:45.320 --> 10:46.270
Listen to me.

10:46.600 --> 10:47.320
Our Xiaolan

10:47.320 --> 10:48.630
is not only beautiful

10:48.910 --> 10:50.750
but also a top student.

10:51.030 --> 10:52.630
She's about
to take the college entrance exam.

10:52.630 --> 10:53.320
The principal of No.1 High School

10:53.320 --> 10:55.080
personally came chasing after her.

10:55.080 --> 10:56.080
And what we sell

10:56.240 --> 10:57.870
are real fashionable goods.

10:58.240 --> 10:59.510
No one wants

10:59.750 --> 11:00.280
the trash

11:00.360 --> 11:01.200
you sell.

11:01.510 --> 11:02.390
What are you saying?

11:02.390 --> 11:03.240
Let me tell you,

11:03.240 --> 11:04.510
shut your mouth.

11:04.630 --> 11:05.630
You look like a dirty rag.

11:05.630 --> 11:06.480
No one wants you.

11:06.480 --> 11:07.320
What are you saying?

11:07.320 --> 11:08.580
I'm talking about you.

11:08.670 --> 11:09.630
I'm talking about you.

11:09.630 --> 11:10.670
Do you understand?

11:10.670 --> 11:11.790
Excuse me. Excuse me.

11:11.790 --> 11:13.120
None of you are good people.

11:13.120 --> 11:13.890
Ladies,

11:13.960 --> 11:14.840
stop arguing.

11:14.870 --> 11:15.720
Who are you?

11:15.790 --> 11:17.120
Mind your own business.

11:17.480 --> 11:18.120
I'm Sun,

11:18.390 --> 11:20.320
the principal of No.1 High School.

11:20.480 --> 11:21.120
Xiaolan

11:21.120 --> 11:22.720
is about to attend our school

11:22.730 --> 11:23.670
to take
the college entrance exam.

11:23.670 --> 11:25.320
I must look after her.

11:26.630 --> 11:28.360
You even hired performers?

11:28.670 --> 11:29.960
He is Mr. Sun.

11:30.200 --> 11:31.840
My niece goes to No.1 High School.

11:31.840 --> 11:33.320
You must be Xia Xiaolan.

11:34.000 --> 11:34.390
Yes.

11:34.660 --> 11:36.080
You passed the placement exam

11:36.080 --> 11:37.360
for No.1 High School.

11:41.340 --> 11:42.050
Do you know

11:42.080 --> 11:43.120
what score she got?

11:43.120 --> 11:44.200
No idea.

11:44.480 --> 11:46.360
446 points!

11:47.890 --> 11:48.600
That exceeds

11:48.600 --> 11:50.510
this year's
bachelor's degree cutoff.

11:50.510 --> 11:51.030
And,

11:51.320 --> 11:52.080
this child's exam paper

11:52.080 --> 11:53.750
still has a lot of room for improvement.

11:53.750 --> 11:54.670
If she revises well,

11:54.670 --> 11:57.840
getting into a key university
next year won't be a problem.

11:57.840 --> 11:58.440
Xiaolan,

11:58.810 --> 11:59.570
let's go

11:59.600 --> 12:01.270
complete the enrollment procedures.

12:01.270 --> 12:01.600
Okay.

12:01.870 --> 12:03.030
Thank you, Mr. Sun.

12:03.390 --> 12:04.320
But

12:05.030 --> 12:06.550
can you let me sell these goods

12:06.550 --> 12:07.240
first?

12:08.550 --> 12:09.510
Xiaolan,

12:09.910 --> 12:11.000
at a time like this,

12:11.000 --> 12:12.030
you're still doing business here?

12:12.030 --> 12:12.720
Mr. Sun,

12:12.720 --> 12:14.080
I didn't know you would be coming today.

12:14.080 --> 12:15.200
I waited at home for several days,

12:15.200 --> 12:16.400
but there was no news.

12:18.150 --> 12:18.840
Qi.

12:20.630 --> 12:21.750
Hello, Xiaolan.

12:22.270 --> 12:23.000
I am Ms. Qi,

12:23.000 --> 12:24.390
who's responsible for grading your exam.

12:24.390 --> 12:25.550
It's due to my mistake

12:25.550 --> 12:26.670
that made you wait for so long.

12:26.670 --> 12:27.600
I apologize.

12:27.630 --> 12:28.120
No need.

12:29.360 --> 12:30.510
Why don't we go to the school

12:30.510 --> 12:31.270
to complete the procedures first?

12:31.270 --> 12:31.930
How's that?

12:32.150 --> 12:33.670
Right. Let's handle the paperwork first.

12:33.670 --> 12:34.730
This is important.

12:34.910 --> 12:35.270
Fen.

12:35.290 --> 12:36.000
You go with her.

12:36.000 --> 12:36.440
Right.

12:36.440 --> 12:37.550
-I'll go with you.
-I'll stay here.

12:37.550 --> 12:38.120
Let's go.

12:38.120 --> 12:38.870
Go on. Hurry up.

12:38.870 --> 12:39.360
Okay.

12:39.750 --> 12:41.390
Come and take a look, everyone.

12:41.390 --> 12:43.000
Our goods are genuine.

12:43.000 --> 12:45.130
Specially brought from Longcheng...

12:46.080 --> 12:46.680
Thank you.

12:46.750 --> 12:47.240
Thank you.

12:47.240 --> 12:48.170
You're welcome.

12:53.360 --> 12:54.150
Thank you both

12:54.150 --> 12:55.410
for taking me seriously.

12:55.410 --> 12:56.690
You've seen

12:56.720 --> 12:57.920
my family situation.

12:57.960 --> 12:58.600
There's something

12:58.600 --> 13:00.200
I'd like to discuss with you.

13:01.110 --> 13:03.120
I will definitely
take the college entrance exam.

13:03.120 --> 13:03.960
But I might not be able

13:03.960 --> 13:04.720
to attend classes at school

13:04.720 --> 13:05.630
this semester.

13:06.320 --> 13:07.080
I would like to

13:07.080 --> 13:08.880
settle my family affairs first.

13:09.120 --> 13:10.650
Otherwise, even if I study,

13:10.750 --> 13:12.080
I won't be able to focus.

13:12.360 --> 13:13.160
But I promise,

13:13.320 --> 13:14.750
I'll definitely return
to school next semester

13:14.750 --> 13:15.950
and revise properly.

13:16.600 --> 13:17.200
Xiaolan.

13:17.670 --> 13:18.800
What are you saying?

13:19.150 --> 13:20.200
I can support you.

13:20.720 --> 13:21.240
Mom.

13:21.440 --> 13:22.120
I know what I'm doing.

13:22.120 --> 13:22.980
I can handle it.

13:23.030 --> 13:24.720
Leave the stall to me.

13:25.080 --> 13:26.200
I can learn slowly.

13:26.480 --> 13:27.200
Trust me.

13:27.390 --> 13:28.480
Didn't I pass the placement exam

13:28.480 --> 13:29.680
through self-study?

13:31.150 --> 13:32.880
Only new players make choices.

13:33.720 --> 13:34.920
I've got a cheat code.

13:34.960 --> 13:36.290
Of course, I want it all.

13:37.120 --> 13:38.240
In this golden age,

13:38.510 --> 13:40.240
whether studying or doing business,

13:40.240 --> 13:41.720
I won't give up on either.

13:42.790 --> 13:43.480
Xiaolan.

13:43.530 --> 13:44.080
I think...

13:44.080 --> 13:44.750
Mr. Sun.

13:45.840 --> 13:46.970
I've made up my mind.

13:47.150 --> 13:47.960
If No.1 High School

13:47.960 --> 13:49.550
cannot accept my study plan,

13:49.550 --> 13:51.150
I can ask at No.2 High School.

13:57.120 --> 13:57.510
Fine.

13:58.150 --> 13:59.960
As long as you're willing
to come to No.1 High School,

13:59.960 --> 14:01.240
I agree to your terms.

14:02.870 --> 14:03.320
Okay.

14:03.550 --> 14:04.610
Thank you, Mr. Sun.

14:10.000 --> 14:11.130
By the way, Xiaolan.

14:11.200 --> 14:12.150
Keep your student ID and meal tickets

14:12.150 --> 14:13.120
safe.

14:13.390 --> 14:14.650
Remember, every week,

14:14.910 --> 14:16.640
you must report to school once.

14:16.900 --> 14:18.270
You must take the monthly exams.

14:18.270 --> 14:18.800
Xiaolan.

14:19.390 --> 14:20.450
Study hard at home.

14:20.510 --> 14:21.440
Don't slack off.

14:21.790 --> 14:23.050
I understand, Mr. Sun.

14:23.440 --> 14:23.770
Good.

14:24.150 --> 14:25.200
You may go home now.

14:25.200 --> 14:25.960
Thank you, Sir.

14:25.960 --> 14:26.960
Thank you, Ma'am.

14:27.960 --> 14:28.490
Let's go.

14:36.790 --> 14:37.650
Xiaolan, look.

14:37.940 --> 14:39.750
Anqing No.1 High School Student ID.

14:39.750 --> 14:41.150
Xia Xiaolan, Grade 12.

14:42.600 --> 14:44.270
Three liang. Six liang.

14:44.600 --> 14:45.260
Nine liang.

14:45.480 --> 14:47.360
So much. I can't count it all.

14:47.550 --> 14:48.200
Auntie,

14:48.430 --> 14:49.950
I think I saw Xia Xiaolan.

14:56.030 --> 14:56.960
Get back to work.

14:57.200 --> 14:58.030
Your sister said,

14:58.030 --> 14:58.840
when she comes back for New Year,

14:58.840 --> 15:00.500
she'll settle it for herself.

15:23.360 --> 15:24.000
Cheng.

15:25.000 --> 15:27.200
Are you really going to repeat the year?

15:27.240 --> 15:28.550
Just to chase a girl,

15:28.550 --> 15:29.840
you're really going all out.

15:29.840 --> 15:31.440
It's truly touching.

15:31.870 --> 15:33.030
It isn't to impress her

15:33.030 --> 15:34.240
that I'm repeating the year.

15:34.240 --> 15:35.600
Her determination woke me up.

15:35.600 --> 15:36.080
Look.

15:37.150 --> 15:37.840
I've been back at school

15:37.840 --> 15:38.700
for 2 weeks now.

15:39.240 --> 15:40.390
I feel more and more that

15:40.390 --> 15:41.510
the decision to keep trying for college

15:41.510 --> 15:42.440
is the right one.

15:43.200 --> 15:45.060
Come with me to Xinhua Bookstore.

15:47.510 --> 15:49.360
These are our usual

15:49.360 --> 15:50.960
exercises and papers.

15:51.630 --> 15:53.080
Mostly English ones.

16:00.440 --> 16:01.360
Also, these are

16:02.270 --> 16:03.080
the notes I took

16:03.080 --> 16:04.120
in class myself.

16:05.000 --> 16:05.840
I saw that you

16:05.840 --> 16:07.170
missed so many classes.

16:07.440 --> 16:08.670
And here are formulas

16:08.670 --> 16:09.870
and things like that.

16:10.160 --> 16:11.630
Some for physics and chemistry,

16:11.630 --> 16:12.560
and English too.

16:13.870 --> 16:15.120
Take this back.

16:16.150 --> 16:17.680
I have my own study methods.

16:17.750 --> 16:19.410
I'll catch up on what I missed.

16:19.630 --> 16:21.030
You need it more than I do.

16:22.000 --> 16:23.120
But you missed so—

16:23.120 --> 16:24.320
Don't you believe me?

16:24.560 --> 16:25.890
If you don't believe me,

16:26.000 --> 16:27.860
let's compare scores next month.

16:31.240 --> 16:32.100
All right then.

16:33.150 --> 16:34.150
Then you look at these,

16:34.150 --> 16:36.000
and I'll take this back for myself.

16:36.000 --> 16:36.910
Okay. Thanks.

16:38.960 --> 16:40.390
I... I-I'll be going.

16:49.440 --> 16:50.030
Chen Qing.

16:50.030 --> 16:50.510
Ma'am.

16:50.620 --> 16:51.050
You're leaving?

16:51.050 --> 16:51.890
I-I'm off.

16:52.520 --> 16:53.360
Not staying for dinner?

16:53.360 --> 16:54.560
No, no, my mom cooked.

16:56.240 --> 16:56.840
Xiaolan.

16:58.080 --> 16:59.030
Why was that kid's face

16:59.030 --> 17:00.120
all flushed red?

17:01.200 --> 17:01.960
You know,

17:02.390 --> 17:03.050
one time,

17:03.080 --> 17:04.500
Chen Qing's mom told me...

17:04.500 --> 17:05.310
-You...
-Auntie,

17:05.310 --> 17:06.349
stop trying to set us up.

17:06.349 --> 17:07.480
I'm not interested.

17:08.200 --> 17:08.960
Okay, okay.

17:09.270 --> 17:10.930
Focus on your revision first.

17:11.079 --> 17:11.510
In college,

17:11.510 --> 17:13.170
there are plenty of good guys.

17:34.400 --> 17:36.480
Chen Qing doesn't know my background.

17:36.480 --> 17:38.280
The 1984 college entrance exam,

17:38.400 --> 17:39.800
I'm determined to ace it.

17:40.960 --> 17:42.480
Apart from my advantage in English,

17:42.480 --> 17:43.000
I have another reason

17:43.000 --> 17:44.330
why I must take the exam.

17:45.240 --> 17:46.970
Because I liked math back then,

17:47.200 --> 17:49.110
I solved every math paper

17:49.110 --> 17:51.970
since the college entrance exams
were reinstated.

17:53.680 --> 17:56.350
I got a very low score on one of them.

18:00.110 --> 18:01.750
1984

18:02.030 --> 18:04.960
National College Entrance Examination
math paper.

18:29.790 --> 18:31.000
After struggling in this hell mode

18:31.000 --> 18:31.880
for so long,

18:32.510 --> 18:34.370
am I finally getting a cheat code?

18:35.510 --> 18:37.200
If I can recall

18:37.350 --> 18:38.510
the hellish

18:38.640 --> 18:40.160
1984 college entrance exam

18:40.160 --> 18:41.480
math paper

18:41.880 --> 18:43.540
and get every question right,

18:43.590 --> 18:45.000
then getting into college

18:45.000 --> 18:46.400
won't be a problem at all.

18:49.390 --> 18:52.940
[Winter, 1983]

18:50.880 --> 18:51.400
Ma'am!

18:53.350 --> 18:54.200
It's you.

18:54.720 --> 18:55.850
You're just in time.

18:56.030 --> 18:56.960
Wait a moment.

19:00.830 --> 19:01.640
Just a second.

19:06.290 --> 19:06.900
This

19:07.070 --> 19:08.320
was sent by the man

19:08.350 --> 19:09.610
who came to eat noodles

19:09.750 --> 19:10.810
with you last time.

19:11.070 --> 19:12.730
He also wrote me a long letter,

19:13.350 --> 19:14.960
telling me again and again

19:15.240 --> 19:17.170
that I must pass these books to you.

19:17.270 --> 19:17.870
By the way,

19:17.930 --> 19:18.960
there is a letter for you too.

19:18.960 --> 19:19.820
This is for you.

19:20.070 --> 19:20.400
Okay.

19:20.420 --> 19:21.790
What noodles do you want today?

19:21.790 --> 19:23.410
Just a bowl of beef noodles.

19:23.500 --> 19:24.350
Alright, wait a moment.

19:24.350 --> 19:25.440
I'll go cook the noodles for you.

19:25.440 --> 19:25.790
Okay.

19:26.680 --> 19:27.680
Cook the noodles!

19:28.350 --> 19:30.350
[To: Xia Xiaolan]

19:38.110 --> 19:39.510
Hello, Comrade Xiaolan.

19:40.030 --> 19:41.160
The last telegram

19:41.510 --> 19:42.640
caused you trouble,

19:43.160 --> 19:43.950
so I didn't dare to rashly

19:43.950 --> 19:45.720
send the letter to the village this time.

19:45.720 --> 19:48.320
I could only ask
the noodle shop owner for help.

19:49.590 --> 19:50.350
Since we parted,

19:50.350 --> 19:52.400
I have been
looking forward to your letter.

19:52.400 --> 19:53.110
Meng! Meng!

19:53.110 --> 19:53.790
No!

19:53.790 --> 19:55.050
Nothing for you today!

19:55.730 --> 19:57.460
I want to know how you are doing.

19:57.480 --> 19:58.610
How is the business?

19:59.000 --> 20:00.200
How are your studies?

20:01.550 --> 20:03.210
I have also returned to the classroom.

20:03.210 --> 20:04.540
I am repeating the year,

20:05.110 --> 20:07.910
preparing for next year's
college entrance exam.

20:09.510 --> 20:10.170
Zhou Cheng!

20:11.070 --> 20:12.330
Let's play for a while.

20:12.790 --> 20:13.480
You guys go ahead.

20:13.480 --> 20:14.280
I'm revising.

20:14.550 --> 20:14.960
Okay.

20:17.110 --> 20:18.550
Last time I saw you only had textbooks

20:18.550 --> 20:19.880
among your study materials,

20:19.880 --> 20:21.750
so I sent the revision materials I'm using

20:21.750 --> 20:23.030
along with this letter.

20:23.030 --> 20:25.070
I hope they'll be of help.

20:27.270 --> 20:29.070
Study life is simple and boring,

20:29.400 --> 20:30.110
but the thought

20:30.110 --> 20:31.700
of you also working hard in Yunan

20:31.700 --> 20:33.030
fills me with strength.

20:38.200 --> 20:40.110
Winter in the capital is beautiful.

20:40.110 --> 20:41.240
If there is a chance,

20:41.400 --> 20:42.800
I really want to show you.

20:43.550 --> 20:45.680
Finally, I hope your studies go well

20:46.160 --> 20:47.360
and you stay healthy.

20:47.590 --> 20:49.320
Looking forward to your reply.

21:06.920 --> 21:07.680
Bro! Bro!

21:07.830 --> 21:08.960
It's me! It's me!

21:09.110 --> 21:10.000
It hurts...

21:11.440 --> 21:13.070
That was so painful.

21:16.480 --> 21:17.680
Why is there a novel?

21:17.920 --> 21:19.590
Aren't you afraid
of affecting her studies?

21:19.590 --> 21:22.000
This is called striking a balance
between work and rest.

21:22.000 --> 21:23.440
With Xiaolan's intelligence,

21:23.440 --> 21:25.220
getting into college is a sure thing.

21:25.220 --> 21:26.080
But do you think

21:26.270 --> 21:28.400
college is the only thing she's after?

21:29.160 --> 21:30.220
What else is there?

21:30.310 --> 21:31.920
The big wide world.

21:34.070 --> 21:34.720
But Cheng,

21:35.110 --> 21:36.200
the books you sent,

21:36.200 --> 21:37.400
did she receive them?

21:37.790 --> 21:38.480
Day in, day out,

21:38.480 --> 21:40.480
you've practically emptied this library,

21:40.480 --> 21:42.610
but you haven't even received a reply.

21:46.550 --> 21:47.160
All right, all right.

21:47.160 --> 21:48.030
Okay. My bad...

21:51.160 --> 21:52.350
What is this?

21:52.650 --> 21:54.170
Shangdu City.

21:54.200 --> 21:55.310
Xia Xiaolan?

21:56.640 --> 21:57.960
Not bad.

21:58.550 --> 22:00.000
Sincerity pays off.

22:00.550 --> 22:01.240
She got 1st place

22:01.240 --> 22:02.680
in her exams.

22:02.960 --> 22:03.690
First place?

22:05.000 --> 22:07.270
For real? Let me see.

22:08.110 --> 22:09.440
Who do you think you are?

22:09.790 --> 22:11.160
Why so stingy?

22:11.350 --> 22:11.750
I'm leaving.

22:11.750 --> 22:12.400
Bro,

22:12.960 --> 22:14.760
you should share the good stuff.

22:15.070 --> 22:15.510
Sir, I'm back.

22:15.510 --> 22:16.110
Happy New Year.

22:16.110 --> 22:16.840
You're back.

22:17.790 --> 22:18.720
Coming through!

22:19.350 --> 22:20.210
Happy New Year.

22:20.350 --> 22:21.110
Happy New Year.

22:21.110 --> 22:21.970
Happy New Year.

22:22.790 --> 22:23.650
Happy New Year.

22:24.680 --> 22:25.350
Uncle Yong,

22:25.720 --> 22:26.780
you struck it rich?

22:26.880 --> 22:28.510
My dad wants you over for a drink.

22:28.510 --> 22:29.550
I'll go in a couple of days.

22:29.550 --> 22:30.160
Okay!

22:31.160 --> 22:31.960
Dayong,

22:32.350 --> 22:33.210
Happy New Year.

22:33.530 --> 22:34.000
By the way,

22:34.000 --> 22:35.240
I heard Xiaolan

22:35.240 --> 22:36.270
scored over 500.

22:36.510 --> 22:38.110
College is in the bag, right?

22:38.270 --> 22:39.870
She still needs to work hard.

22:40.270 --> 22:41.000
Come on.

22:41.000 --> 22:41.930
Quick, sit down.

22:42.030 --> 22:43.350
Raise your glasses, everyone.

22:43.350 --> 22:45.680
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

22:51.240 --> 22:53.750
Happiness was sealed in the past.

22:55.030 --> 22:56.640
Or perhaps it is right here.

22:57.920 --> 23:00.320
Even though there are many hardships here.

23:00.960 --> 23:01.720
Poverty.

23:02.240 --> 23:03.100
Backwardness.

23:03.510 --> 23:04.440
And a beginning trapped in

23:04.440 --> 23:05.830
a quagmire of rumors.

23:07.280 --> 23:08.680
But it is also wonderful.

23:09.110 --> 23:09.750
Because

23:10.880 --> 23:11.940
I have a home again.

23:29.930 --> 23:30.730
You're awake.

23:31.110 --> 23:32.130
Morning, Mom!

23:32.350 --> 23:32.880
Morning.

23:33.160 --> 23:34.020
Happy New Year.

23:34.160 --> 23:36.110
-Happy New Year.
-Happy New Year.

23:37.960 --> 23:38.640
Xiaolan.

23:40.070 --> 23:41.200
It's New Year's Day.

23:41.400 --> 23:42.030
The whole family

23:42.030 --> 23:43.640
is going to the fair together.

23:43.640 --> 23:45.350
I was trying to talk your mom into it,

23:45.350 --> 23:46.550
but she refused to go.

23:47.160 --> 23:48.760
I don't like crowded places.

23:49.480 --> 23:50.350
It's the New Year.

23:50.350 --> 23:51.400
It's nice to be somewhere lively.

23:51.400 --> 23:52.200
You have to go.

23:52.480 --> 23:54.340
Xiaolan, I'm leaving this to you.

23:54.880 --> 23:55.310
Okay.

23:55.590 --> 23:55.960
Hey!

23:56.990 --> 23:58.590
The Li family mentioned it yesterday.

23:58.590 --> 23:59.200
Do you know how much

23:59.200 --> 24:00.200
a bowl of noodles there is?

24:00.200 --> 24:01.030
6 dimes.

24:01.240 --> 24:02.720
It was only 4 dimes last year.

24:02.720 --> 24:04.000
Why join the crowd?

24:06.550 --> 24:07.550
Mom, take this.

24:08.240 --> 24:08.640
Hey!

24:08.920 --> 24:09.850
What is this for?

24:09.880 --> 24:11.110
It's not that you don't like

24:11.110 --> 24:12.230
crowded places.

24:12.480 --> 24:13.240
You just don't like going

24:13.240 --> 24:14.700
to places that cost money.

24:16.370 --> 24:17.510
I can't take this money.

24:17.510 --> 24:18.480
It's hard-earned money. Take it.

24:18.480 --> 24:20.200
Since it's hard-earned money,

24:20.200 --> 24:20.720
if you save it up and don't spend it,

24:20.720 --> 24:22.450
it'll just sit at home and mold.

24:22.560 --> 24:23.190
If you earn but don't spend,

24:23.190 --> 24:24.720
isn't life just suffering?

24:25.070 --> 24:25.800
Listen to me.

24:25.960 --> 24:26.830
Don't save for me.

24:26.830 --> 24:27.680
If you don't spend it all today,

24:27.680 --> 24:28.610
don't come back.

24:30.310 --> 24:30.720
Okay.

24:31.680 --> 24:32.740
I'll listen to you.

24:33.400 --> 24:34.400
Now that's right.

24:35.550 --> 24:36.380
Hurry and wash your face.

24:36.380 --> 24:37.240
I'll go tidy up.

24:37.640 --> 24:38.030
Okay.

24:48.030 --> 24:49.270
In the past, when Auntie took Cousin

24:49.270 --> 24:50.500
to the amusement park,

24:50.500 --> 24:52.160
I always said I didn't like it.

24:52.960 --> 24:54.350
But how could that be true?

24:54.350 --> 24:56.550
I was just a child back then.

24:58.110 --> 24:59.830
Living under someone else's roof,

24:59.830 --> 25:01.200
I was afraid of spending money

25:01.200 --> 25:02.550
and causing trouble.

25:03.200 --> 25:04.260
Living life again,

25:04.830 --> 25:06.430
not only will I live happily,

25:06.640 --> 25:08.440
but I also want my family and friends

25:08.440 --> 25:09.370
to live happily.

25:19.500 --> 25:23.870
♪ Blow, blow, let the wind blow ♪

25:23.890 --> 25:29.230
♪ Wipe away the glistening tears
in your eyes ♪

25:27.960 --> 25:28.640
Lion dance!

25:29.260 --> 25:33.960
♪ Blow, blow, let the wind blow ♪

25:33.510 --> 25:34.590
How much is this?

25:34.280 --> 25:40.250
♪ Take away all the sadness;
no matter who it is in the wind ♪

25:36.590 --> 25:38.520
Look, there's popcorn over there.

25:39.110 --> 25:39.910
I want popcorn

25:40.000 --> 25:40.790
and rice crisps.

25:40.790 --> 25:41.350
One bag of each.

25:41.350 --> 25:41.950
All right.

25:54.750 --> 25:55.920
It really feels like New Year.

25:55.920 --> 25:57.720
There are sugar paintings here.

25:57.780 --> 25:58.540
I want one.

25:58.720 --> 26:00.050
How much is this, Ma'am?

26:00.130 --> 26:00.860
2 dimes each.

26:01.100 --> 26:01.430
Sure.

26:03.240 --> 26:03.920
-Here.
-Okay.

26:03.920 --> 26:04.830
Okay, come on. Spin it, miss.

26:04.830 --> 26:05.290
Spin it.

26:06.350 --> 26:07.030
A butterfly.

26:07.030 --> 26:07.690
Butterfly.

26:10.960 --> 26:11.780
Fish! Fish!

26:11.880 --> 26:13.280
Let's go look at the fish!

26:13.640 --> 26:14.920
They're huge.

26:15.160 --> 26:15.790
Come take a look.

26:15.790 --> 26:16.680
Fish from Baixi Reservoir.

26:16.680 --> 26:17.810
They're very fresh.

26:17.830 --> 26:18.510
These big ones

26:18.510 --> 26:19.160
are 15 each.

26:19.160 --> 26:20.480
15 each?

26:20.480 --> 26:21.740
That's too expensive.

26:21.750 --> 26:22.880
It's not expensive. Buy it.

26:22.880 --> 26:24.030
It's New Year. We'll take one.

26:24.030 --> 26:24.680
Such a big fish,

26:24.680 --> 26:26.110
we can't cook like restaurants do.

26:26.110 --> 26:27.770
It'd be a waste if we bought it.

26:28.590 --> 26:29.390
Here, take it.

26:29.520 --> 26:30.350
All right, all right.

26:30.350 --> 26:31.350
Such an expensive

26:31.590 --> 26:32.680
and huge fish!

26:32.680 --> 26:33.440
Mrs. Chen.

26:33.510 --> 26:34.590
Mrs. Chen, Happy New Year!

26:34.590 --> 26:35.450
Happy New Year!

26:35.720 --> 26:36.480
Happy New Year!

26:36.480 --> 26:37.440
Everyone is out for a stroll?

26:37.440 --> 26:38.070
Yes, yes.

26:38.070 --> 26:39.130
Let's go together.

26:39.180 --> 26:40.510
Keep the biggest one for me.

26:40.510 --> 26:41.510
Don't worry!

26:54.920 --> 26:56.580
Jianhua, I'm getting hungry.

26:56.640 --> 26:57.790
Go buy me a bun.

26:59.120 --> 27:00.030
Wait for me here then.

27:00.030 --> 27:00.360
Okay.

27:08.160 --> 27:08.640
Ma'am,

27:08.790 --> 27:09.440
I'd like a bun.

27:09.440 --> 27:09.880
Sure.

27:10.650 --> 27:11.800
This one looks nice.

27:11.830 --> 27:12.200
Here.

27:12.350 --> 27:12.880
Try it.

27:13.270 --> 27:13.870
Tao, come.

27:14.240 --> 27:14.900
Looks good.

27:37.030 --> 27:38.360
What are you smiling at?

27:40.640 --> 27:42.300
I saw you working in the fields

27:42.300 --> 27:43.140
all day today.

27:43.480 --> 27:45.160
I filled a basin of water for you.

27:45.160 --> 27:46.310
Wash up.

27:47.070 --> 27:47.750
Thank you.

27:52.640 --> 27:53.160
By the way,

27:53.160 --> 27:55.220
there's a movie in the village today.

27:55.400 --> 27:56.860
I'll go save a seat in a bit.

27:56.880 --> 27:58.880
Otherwise, we won't get a good spot.

27:59.000 --> 27:59.350
Okay.

27:59.400 --> 28:01.060
I'll change my clothes first.

28:01.110 --> 28:02.200
I worked all day

28:02.200 --> 28:02.960
and I stink.

28:03.160 --> 28:04.590
I don't want to smell bad around you.

28:04.590 --> 28:05.000
Okay.

28:12.580 --> 28:14.700
[To: Xia Xiaolan]

28:19.270 --> 28:19.880
Jianhua.

28:20.000 --> 28:21.330
Xiaolan, why did you...

28:24.480 --> 28:25.400
Z-Ziyu.

28:26.200 --> 28:27.330
Is something wrong?

28:51.880 --> 28:52.750
This is delicious.

28:52.750 --> 28:53.400
Right?

28:54.000 --> 28:55.240
Theirs is the best.

28:55.440 --> 28:56.590
Come on, let's buy some too.

28:56.590 --> 28:57.510
Buy some.

28:57.550 --> 28:57.920
What?

28:59.110 --> 28:59.640
I'll pay. Let me get it.

28:59.640 --> 29:00.240
No need, it's fine.

29:00.240 --> 29:00.720
I'll buy it.

29:00.720 --> 29:01.510
No, no.

29:01.750 --> 29:03.590
Don't. You pay every time.

29:04.160 --> 29:04.590
Ziyu.

29:05.200 --> 29:06.350
Try it. Eat it while it's hot.

29:06.350 --> 29:06.920
This child.

29:06.920 --> 29:08.240
This kid is so pretty.

29:08.550 --> 29:09.440
Say thank you.

29:11.750 --> 29:12.280
How is it?

29:13.400 --> 29:14.000
It's not good.

29:14.000 --> 29:15.440
I won't eat it. You have it.

29:15.440 --> 29:17.040
Weren't you hungry just now?

29:17.160 --> 29:19.070
She's just like her mother.

29:24.240 --> 29:24.830
Xiaolan.

29:25.070 --> 29:26.310
Let's go look over there.

29:26.310 --> 29:27.110
Right. Let's go.

29:27.110 --> 29:28.640
Didn't we already go there?

29:28.720 --> 29:31.450
Let's just look around here.
It's fine. Let's go.

29:31.790 --> 29:32.910
Ziyu, let's go.

29:33.680 --> 29:35.410
Why leave? What's the big deal?

29:49.240 --> 29:49.830
Xiaolan.

29:53.350 --> 29:54.350
It's New Year.

29:55.270 --> 29:57.270
Since you insist on provoking me...

29:59.330 --> 30:00.040
Chen Qing.

30:00.550 --> 30:01.880
Take Tao to play for a while.

30:01.880 --> 30:03.350
Tao, let's go play.

30:04.270 --> 30:05.470
Mom, come with me too.

30:05.720 --> 30:06.590
I didn't bring money.

30:06.590 --> 30:07.000
I...

30:10.110 --> 30:11.710
Xia Ziyu, why did you call me?

30:12.070 --> 30:13.330
Except for an apology,

30:13.750 --> 30:14.400
what else do you have

30:14.400 --> 30:15.200
to say to me?

30:16.000 --> 30:17.000
Apologize?

30:17.000 --> 30:18.800
You should look like you mean it.

30:19.000 --> 30:20.310
Who are you

30:20.310 --> 30:21.570
pulling a long face at?

30:22.920 --> 30:23.480
Auntie.

30:23.710 --> 30:24.570
Happy New Year.

30:25.000 --> 30:26.160
Forget it. Forget it.

30:26.160 --> 30:28.300
We dare not be the auntie
of a Golden Phoenix.

30:28.300 --> 30:29.480
I don't have that luck.

30:29.480 --> 30:30.740
Just say what you want.

30:31.510 --> 30:32.110
Xiaolan.

30:32.880 --> 30:34.030
Your sister didn't do anything

30:34.030 --> 30:34.960
to wrong you.

30:35.490 --> 30:36.550
If there is a fault,

30:36.640 --> 30:37.800
it is mine.

30:38.590 --> 30:39.480
I chose

30:39.480 --> 30:40.740
to be with your sister,

30:41.110 --> 30:42.750
and I don't regret it at all.

30:43.550 --> 30:44.730
Ziyu meant well.

30:45.230 --> 30:46.360
She wanted to say hi.

30:51.310 --> 30:52.590
Don't look at my mother.

30:52.590 --> 30:53.440
My mother isn't

30:53.440 --> 30:55.170
a pushover you can manipulate.

30:55.270 --> 30:55.900
Xia Ziyu.

30:56.110 --> 30:57.640
What act are you putting on?

30:57.790 --> 30:58.960
There is a stage right here.

30:58.960 --> 31:00.190
Why don't you go up and act

31:00.190 --> 31:01.310
to perform for everyone?

31:01.310 --> 31:02.680
Don't waste everyone's time at the market.

31:02.680 --> 31:03.240
Right?

31:04.270 --> 31:04.960
Xiaolan.

31:05.110 --> 31:06.350
Jianhua is right.

31:06.750 --> 31:08.270
I really just wanted to say hi to you

31:08.270 --> 31:08.930
and Auntie.

31:10.000 --> 31:12.260
There is a misunderstanding between us.

31:12.350 --> 31:13.400
But I hope

31:13.400 --> 31:15.930
you won't take it out
on the rest of the family.

31:16.030 --> 31:17.790
Can you go back and see Uncle?

31:18.310 --> 31:20.240
He misses you and Auntie very much.

31:21.400 --> 31:23.130
You have to think about Auntie.

31:24.300 --> 31:25.240
Running back to her parents' home

31:25.240 --> 31:26.480
is not the solution.

31:27.750 --> 31:28.550
Wait a moment.

31:29.160 --> 31:30.620
That's not the main point.

31:30.830 --> 31:33.200
We aren't done with the business
between the three of us.

31:33.200 --> 31:33.920
What's between the three of us

31:33.920 --> 31:35.160
is not a misunderstanding.

31:35.160 --> 31:36.110
Didn't Wang Jianhua

31:36.110 --> 31:37.400
admit it for you?

31:37.920 --> 31:39.880
He wronged me.

31:40.720 --> 31:42.110
You stole my boyfriend.

31:42.830 --> 31:43.440
Xia Ziyu.

31:43.790 --> 31:45.110
Do you admit this or not?

31:45.110 --> 31:46.200
If you insist on putting it that way,

31:46.200 --> 31:47.600
there is nothing I can do.

31:48.110 --> 31:49.200
But regardless,

31:49.680 --> 31:51.480
Uncle didn't do anything wrong.

31:51.640 --> 31:52.550
As long as you agree

31:52.550 --> 31:54.480
for Uncle and Auntie to reconcile,

31:54.640 --> 31:56.170
I'm willing to do anything.

31:56.540 --> 31:58.030
You're really willing to do anything?

31:58.030 --> 31:59.160
As long as I can do it.

32:00.850 --> 32:01.980
Then you really are

32:02.030 --> 32:03.590
being too insincere.

32:04.200 --> 32:06.070
You saw me a while ago.

32:06.440 --> 32:07.510
You hesitated there for a long time,

32:07.510 --> 32:08.350
and finally decided

32:08.350 --> 32:10.270
to come up and act out this sob story.

32:10.270 --> 32:11.640
You just wanted to act generous

32:11.640 --> 32:12.770
in front of your man.

32:13.070 --> 32:14.830
But you didn't expect me
to see through it.

32:14.830 --> 32:16.230
Now you're acting again,

32:16.270 --> 32:17.200
trying to make others think

32:17.200 --> 32:18.440
that my mother
ran back to her parents' home

32:18.440 --> 32:19.900
because of her bad temper.

32:20.030 --> 32:20.690
Xia Ziyu,

32:21.070 --> 32:22.440
is this really necessary?

32:22.440 --> 32:22.830
Xiaolan,

32:22.830 --> 32:24.560
I really didn't think that way.

32:25.310 --> 32:27.170
Did you really not think that way?

32:28.200 --> 32:28.820
Xia Ziyu.

32:29.200 --> 32:29.960
Do you know,

32:30.550 --> 32:31.990
if you want to be a villain,

32:31.990 --> 32:33.510
there's no need to put up so much of an act.

32:33.510 --> 32:35.770
Otherwise, you'll be written out early.

32:36.350 --> 32:37.350
I originally just wanted

32:37.350 --> 32:37.920
to see

32:37.920 --> 32:39.450
what kind of person you are.

32:40.200 --> 32:41.160
But now,

32:41.720 --> 32:42.550
I'm sorry,

32:43.070 --> 32:44.330
you really disgust me.

32:45.100 --> 32:45.830
Xia Xiaolan,

32:46.240 --> 32:47.160
don't go too far.

32:47.160 --> 32:48.030
What are you trying to do?

32:48.030 --> 32:49.630
Don't you lay a finger on her!

32:53.270 --> 32:54.130
That's Liu Fen.

32:54.400 --> 32:54.860
Liu Fen—

32:54.960 --> 32:55.550
Liu Yong?

32:56.030 --> 32:57.160
What are they doing?

32:57.240 --> 32:58.480
Bullying our girl?

32:59.640 --> 33:00.510
What are you doing?

33:00.510 --> 33:01.680
What are you doing?

33:01.960 --> 33:03.020
What are you doing?

33:03.240 --> 33:03.720
What are you doing?

33:03.720 --> 33:05.070
-What are you doing?
-What?

33:05.070 --> 33:05.830
What are you doing?

33:05.830 --> 33:06.720
You want to bully us, don't you?

33:06.720 --> 33:07.400
We didn't bully anyone!

33:07.400 --> 33:08.000
What do you want?

33:08.000 --> 33:08.720
You tell me.

33:09.160 --> 33:10.110
Ganging up to bully us.

33:10.110 --> 33:11.030
What do you mean?

33:11.030 --> 33:11.920
Who is bullying whom?

33:11.920 --> 33:13.250
There are so many of you.

33:13.310 --> 33:13.830
It's the New Year.

33:13.830 --> 33:14.480
What's going on here?

33:14.480 --> 33:15.160
Seriously.

33:15.160 --> 33:16.750
Can't we talk about this nicely?

33:16.750 --> 33:18.550
What's wrong, Comrade Xiaolan?

33:19.720 --> 33:20.830
Who are these two?

33:22.880 --> 33:24.880
Isn't that my "Golden Phoenix" cousin

33:24.880 --> 33:26.140
and my cousin-in-law?

33:28.000 --> 33:30.350
Xia Ziyu and Wang Jianhua?

33:31.440 --> 33:32.960
Xiaolan took good care of you, didn't she?

33:32.960 --> 33:34.890
Now you've found a new meal ticket?

33:35.830 --> 33:36.270
By the way,

33:36.270 --> 33:37.070
Wang Jianhua,

33:37.590 --> 33:40.270
your round-trip travel expenses,

33:40.270 --> 33:42.110
food and boarding expenses,
and transport costs back then,

33:42.110 --> 33:43.400
I paid for all of that, didn't I?

33:43.400 --> 33:44.800
Then you suddenly told me

33:44.830 --> 33:46.490
you wanted to be with Xia Ziyu.

33:46.490 --> 33:47.200
In that case,

33:47.200 --> 33:48.660
pay me back my money first.

33:49.070 --> 33:50.450
I've calculated it for you.

33:50.450 --> 33:51.970
It's 35 yuan in total.

33:52.000 --> 33:52.920
I rounded it down.

33:52.920 --> 33:53.960
I'm not taking advantage of you.

33:53.960 --> 33:54.440
Pay up.

33:54.550 --> 33:55.110
What's going on?

33:55.110 --> 33:56.000
Take it out.

33:56.030 --> 33:56.760
Is that true?

33:57.270 --> 33:58.200
What's going on?

34:00.160 --> 34:01.480
Wh-What's going on?

34:04.430 --> 34:05.560
Wh-What's going on?

34:21.960 --> 34:22.440
Here!

34:22.440 --> 34:23.500
What are you doing?

34:23.800 --> 34:24.600
Give it to her!

34:25.710 --> 34:26.440
Xia Xiaolan.

34:26.840 --> 34:28.150
If insulting me like this

34:28.150 --> 34:29.550
is what it takes for you to cool off,

34:29.550 --> 34:31.219
I'll pay the money for Jianhua.

34:31.219 --> 34:33.199
Xia Ziyu, you're so generous.

34:33.590 --> 34:34.800
That 35 yuan

34:34.800 --> 34:36.360
took me years to save.

34:36.800 --> 34:37.440
But you?

34:37.920 --> 34:39.920
The whole family supports just you.

34:40.150 --> 34:41.000
You took out

34:41.000 --> 34:42.000
this 35 yuan

34:42.000 --> 34:42.760
so easily.

34:44.960 --> 34:46.360
I don't want what's extra.

34:46.360 --> 34:48.020
Have fun supporting your man.

34:48.460 --> 34:49.830
W-Watch your mouth.

34:53.360 --> 34:54.520
Let's go.

34:55.400 --> 34:55.960
Hurry up.

34:56.800 --> 34:57.760
Serves you right.

34:57.760 --> 34:58.360
Show's over!

34:58.360 --> 34:59.110
Show's over!

34:59.590 --> 35:01.280
So annoying.

35:01.480 --> 35:03.080
Now we have money to buy fish.

35:03.760 --> 35:04.150
Mom,

35:04.400 --> 35:05.600
let me introduce you.

35:05.710 --> 35:06.510
This is Zhou Cheng,

35:06.510 --> 35:07.920
the person who helped me before.

35:07.920 --> 35:08.590
Hello, Ma'am.

35:08.590 --> 35:09.360
Zhou Cheng,

35:09.480 --> 35:10.320
thank you for helping Xiaolan.

35:10.320 --> 35:11.190
Not at all. It was the right thing to do.

35:11.190 --> 35:12.280
You saved the day today.

35:12.280 --> 35:13.070
Let's go. I'm treating you to a meal.

35:13.070 --> 35:13.440
Yeah, yeah.

35:13.440 --> 35:13.880
What do you want to eat?

35:13.880 --> 35:14.190
Let's go.

35:14.190 --> 35:15.520
Let's go eat at our home.

35:20.320 --> 35:21.280
Happy New Year!

35:21.440 --> 35:22.300
Happy New Year!

35:23.510 --> 35:26.110
We're home.

35:26.880 --> 35:28.000
Thank you.

35:28.000 --> 35:28.840
Slow down.

35:29.400 --> 35:30.860
Come here, let me hold you.

35:31.320 --> 35:31.850
Let's go.

35:32.590 --> 35:33.190
Let's go.

35:34.030 --> 35:34.510
Thanks.

35:36.640 --> 35:37.360
Happy New Year!

35:37.360 --> 35:38.290
Dayong, Dayong.

35:38.800 --> 35:39.730
You have guests?

35:41.400 --> 35:42.590
Fengmei's relatives.

35:42.590 --> 35:43.110
Right.

35:43.230 --> 35:44.400
My nephew.

35:45.000 --> 35:46.110
No wonder I haven't seen him before.

35:46.110 --> 35:46.900
It's for me?

35:48.710 --> 35:49.400
What are you doing?

35:49.400 --> 35:51.150
It's for my father-in-law.

35:51.880 --> 35:52.510
See you later.

35:52.510 --> 35:53.130
See you.

36:13.070 --> 36:13.630
Xiaolan.

36:14.190 --> 36:15.320
What are you making?

36:16.230 --> 36:17.670
One fish, four ways to eat.

36:17.670 --> 36:19.110
Watch and learn.

36:23.630 --> 36:25.160
I've never had it like this.

36:25.360 --> 36:26.000
Try some later.

36:26.000 --> 36:27.000
It's really good.

36:35.260 --> 36:35.760
Let me do it, Auntie.

36:35.760 --> 36:36.440
No need, Zhou.

36:36.440 --> 36:37.190
Go to the kitchen.

36:37.190 --> 36:38.400
Help Xiaolan.

36:38.740 --> 36:39.150
Okay.

36:44.690 --> 36:45.280
This young man

36:45.280 --> 36:47.280
is really handsome.

36:48.030 --> 36:49.670
Xiaolan is pretty too.

36:51.440 --> 36:52.440
It smells so good.

36:52.920 --> 36:53.950
Not bad, Xiaolan.

36:54.660 --> 36:57.320
Don't just stand there.
Peel some garlic for me.

36:58.680 --> 36:59.520
Look at him,

36:59.550 --> 37:01.230
coming to our house during the New Year.

37:01.230 --> 37:02.400
Is he interested

37:02.400 --> 37:03.060
in our Xiaolan?

37:03.060 --> 37:04.330
He is definitely interested.

37:04.330 --> 37:05.660
He confessed directly.

37:06.000 --> 37:06.880
He wants to pursue Xiaolan

37:06.880 --> 37:07.630
and date her.

37:10.360 --> 37:11.560
But Xiaolan refused.

37:11.840 --> 37:12.900
She was very clear.

37:13.080 --> 37:14.410
Studies come first.

37:14.440 --> 37:15.670
She doesn't want anything else.

37:15.670 --> 37:17.200
But the kid hasn't given up.

37:20.840 --> 37:22.030
Coming!

37:22.800 --> 37:24.260
One fish, four ways to eat.

37:25.590 --> 37:26.280
Dinner is served!

37:26.280 --> 37:26.880
Let's eat!

37:27.550 --> 37:29.320
I want that fish ball.

37:29.510 --> 37:30.880
Look at you, so impatient.

37:30.880 --> 37:32.110
We have a guest today.

37:32.410 --> 37:33.440
He hasn't eaten yet.

37:33.440 --> 37:34.640
It's okay. Here, Tao.

37:35.150 --> 37:35.510
Here.

37:36.370 --> 37:36.770
Look.

37:36.800 --> 37:37.760
Thank you!

37:37.800 --> 37:39.710
Let's have a toast first.

37:39.710 --> 37:40.280
Right. Come on.

37:40.280 --> 37:41.320
Xiaolan is amazing.

37:41.320 --> 37:42.480
She made all this.

37:42.480 --> 37:42.840
Come on.

37:42.840 --> 37:44.120
Welcome, Zhou.

37:44.150 --> 37:44.710
Great.

37:44.760 --> 37:45.960
-Cheers.
-Thank you.

37:49.030 --> 37:49.960
Zhou.

37:50.990 --> 37:53.450
Still delivering goods
during the New Year?

37:54.190 --> 37:55.630
I don't deliver goods anymore.

37:55.630 --> 37:56.690
Just like Xiaolan,

37:56.890 --> 37:57.800
I'm repeating the year

37:57.800 --> 38:00.190
preparing for next year's
college entrance exams.

38:00.190 --> 38:01.720
You're taking the exam too?

38:05.150 --> 38:06.760
We are basically

38:06.760 --> 38:08.490
long-distance study buddies.

38:08.960 --> 38:09.940
What does that mean?

38:09.940 --> 38:10.600
What buddy?

38:10.960 --> 38:11.660
Long-distance.

38:11.660 --> 38:13.080
It means two different places.

38:13.080 --> 38:14.520
He sent me

38:14.550 --> 38:16.400
a lot of study materials recently.

38:16.400 --> 38:18.030
It's been very helpful.

38:18.360 --> 38:18.960
Besides,

38:19.190 --> 38:20.320
he helped us

38:20.320 --> 38:21.320
with the situation today.

38:21.320 --> 38:22.360
So inviting him to dinner

38:22.360 --> 38:23.690
is the least we could do.

38:23.880 --> 38:24.680
That's right.

38:24.710 --> 38:25.320
Thank you, Zhou.

38:25.320 --> 38:26.360
Welcome. Come on.

38:26.360 --> 38:26.840
You're welcome, Ma'am.

38:26.840 --> 38:27.700
Have some fish.

38:28.030 --> 38:29.400
Thank you, Ma'am.

38:29.400 --> 38:30.000
I'll help myself.

38:30.000 --> 38:30.460
This...

38:30.550 --> 38:31.800
Zhou, have some fish.

38:31.920 --> 38:33.400
He can help himself.

38:33.400 --> 38:34.590
He's a big young man.

38:34.920 --> 38:36.180
We are classmates now.

38:36.280 --> 38:36.960
We help each other.

38:36.960 --> 38:37.360
Right.

38:37.590 --> 38:37.880
Good.

38:37.880 --> 38:39.670
Helping each other
and making progress together.

38:39.670 --> 38:40.870
What a perfect match.

38:44.990 --> 38:46.100
I... I mean

38:46.320 --> 38:48.630
a perfect match as study partners.

38:48.880 --> 38:49.610
Look at them.

38:49.840 --> 38:50.400
Learning from each other.

38:50.400 --> 38:51.800
Eat up, eat up.

38:52.360 --> 38:52.800
I...

38:53.070 --> 38:53.960
Here, Fengmei.

38:54.320 --> 38:55.760
Auntie, have some vegetables.

38:55.760 --> 38:56.360
Okay.

38:56.670 --> 38:57.480
I'll eat.

39:00.880 --> 39:01.670
Zhou Cheng.

39:01.880 --> 39:03.590
You're still staying at that guesthouse,

39:03.590 --> 39:04.030
right?

39:04.160 --> 39:05.110
Yes, I'm still staying there.

39:05.110 --> 39:06.400
I'll take you back

39:06.400 --> 39:07.330
on my bike later.

39:08.360 --> 39:08.800
Okay.

39:09.480 --> 39:10.340
Thank you, Sir.

39:11.920 --> 39:13.320
Come on, have a drink.

39:14.120 --> 39:14.770
Cheers.

39:14.800 --> 39:15.280
Sir.

39:21.670 --> 39:22.630
Pour it.

39:23.280 --> 39:24.210
What did you say?

39:25.030 --> 39:27.320
That's 35 yuan,

39:27.320 --> 39:28.780
and you just gave it to her?

39:31.230 --> 39:32.560
Grandma, it's my fault.

39:33.020 --> 39:34.550
I didn't protect Ziyu well.

39:34.710 --> 39:35.360
Jianhua.

39:35.800 --> 39:36.920
It's not your fault.

39:36.920 --> 39:38.320
I don't blame Xiaolan either.

39:38.320 --> 39:39.650
That's just her temper.

39:40.070 --> 39:40.880
I'm used to it.

39:41.510 --> 39:43.170
You're used to it, but I'm not.

39:44.150 --> 39:45.510
She's out of control.

39:46.320 --> 39:47.850
We must get that money back.

39:48.110 --> 39:49.840
I thought going to school

39:49.840 --> 39:51.110
would make her better.

39:51.130 --> 39:51.770
Who knew

39:51.960 --> 39:53.960
she's still an ungrateful wretch.

39:54.590 --> 39:55.590
I'm furious.

40:00.150 --> 40:00.710
Mother.

40:02.070 --> 40:02.880
It's the New Year.

40:02.880 --> 40:04.140
Don't get so worked up.

40:04.480 --> 40:06.030
Look, it's the New Year.

40:07.360 --> 40:08.430
Our Ziyu...

40:08.670 --> 40:10.400
You watched her grow up.

40:11.120 --> 40:12.370
You know

40:12.400 --> 40:13.660
her temperament best.

40:14.320 --> 40:15.880
Honest, kind,

40:16.190 --> 40:17.250
and good-hearted.

40:17.440 --> 40:18.970
Doesn't she take after you?

40:19.360 --> 40:21.550
She always thinks of the family.

40:23.150 --> 40:23.810
You know...

40:24.510 --> 40:25.760
Mother, don't blame me.

40:25.760 --> 40:27.960
I shouldn't be doing this on New Year...

40:28.230 --> 40:29.630
You guys go ahead and eat.

40:29.960 --> 40:30.960
I really can't bear

40:30.960 --> 40:32.030
to see Second Uncle and Second Aunt

40:32.030 --> 40:33.160
fighting like this.

40:33.920 --> 40:34.720
Second Uncle.

40:35.040 --> 40:35.710
You and Second Aunt

40:35.710 --> 40:37.400
haven't seen each other for so long.

40:37.400 --> 40:39.530
There must be some misunderstanding.

40:44.440 --> 40:45.070
Grandma.

40:45.710 --> 40:47.190
Xiaolan is still a Xia.

40:48.630 --> 40:49.430
Second Uncle.

40:49.570 --> 40:50.770
Xiaolan is stubborn.

40:50.970 --> 40:51.960
If she could come back,

40:51.960 --> 40:53.280
it would be better than anything.

40:53.280 --> 40:54.360
Please don't mention

40:54.360 --> 40:56.020
anything about apologizing.

40:56.150 --> 40:57.880
She is studying at No.1 High School now.

40:57.880 --> 40:58.670
If Second Uncle and Second Aunt

40:58.670 --> 41:00.070
could get back together,

41:00.510 --> 41:02.170
Xiaolan could study in peace.

41:02.620 --> 41:04.880
She's staying with her maternal uncle,
after all.

41:04.880 --> 41:06.480
That's living under someone else's roof.

41:06.480 --> 41:08.410
How could she focus on her studies?

41:09.150 --> 41:10.960
Her life must be difficult.

41:36.880 --> 41:37.540
Zhou Cheng.

41:38.590 --> 41:39.000
Uncle.

41:39.290 --> 41:40.400
The rain is so heavy.

41:40.400 --> 41:41.800
How are you getting back?

41:43.360 --> 41:44.070
Yeah.

41:44.710 --> 41:46.370
It really is coming down hard.

41:47.320 --> 41:48.450
If you can't go back,

41:49.100 --> 41:50.430
stay with Tao and me

41:50.460 --> 41:51.210
tonight.

41:51.360 --> 41:52.160
Don't go back.

41:53.630 --> 41:54.280
Xiaolan,

41:54.760 --> 41:56.520
can your aunt sleep with you?

41:57.230 --> 41:57.670
Sure.

41:59.360 --> 42:00.000
Fengmei!

42:00.800 --> 42:02.540
Zhou Cheng is staying here tonight!

42:02.540 --> 42:03.600
Get an extra quilt!

42:04.000 --> 42:04.600
All right!

42:05.760 --> 42:06.620
Thank you, Sir.

42:10.960 --> 42:11.760
Are you happy?

42:15.550 --> 42:16.610
Let me do it. Let me.

42:34.760 --> 42:35.690
Have some water.

42:35.710 --> 42:36.770
Careful, it's hot.

42:41.510 --> 42:42.970
I'm sorry you had to suffer

42:43.230 --> 42:44.360
through this today.

42:46.070 --> 42:46.670
Jianhua,

42:47.280 --> 42:48.940
please don't think like that.

42:49.070 --> 42:49.760
Actually, I think

42:49.760 --> 42:51.160
it turned out fine today.

42:51.670 --> 42:53.190
You returned the money to her.

42:53.190 --> 42:54.800
From now on, you don't owe her anything.
